text: Cratena tema is a species of sea slug, an aeolid nudibranch, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Facelinidae.MolluscaBase (2018). Cratena tema Edmunds, 2015. Accessed on 2018-02-18. ==Distribution== This species was described from Ghana. ==References== Category:Facelinidae Category:Gastropods described in 2015
